headline.main: UN Says 66,000 Displaced in 5 Months of North Syria Fighting
headline.print_headline: UN Says 66,000 Displaced in 5 Months of North Syria Fighting

lead_paragraph: Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said he would meet Russian President Vladimir Putin in Moscow on Thursday to voice opposition to what the Israeli leader charged were Iran's attempts to establish a permanent military foothold in Syria.
